# Naming Conventions

## Java
- Classes: `PascalCase` — `PreShiftCheck`, `ApiResponse`, `DateTimeUtils`
- Methods/variables: `camelCase` — `rosterDate`, `nowUtc()`
- Constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE` — `MINUTES_IN_DAY`, `TIME_FORMATTER`
- Packages: `lowercase` — `entities`, `dtos`, `services`

## Entities & Tables
- Entity class: singular noun — `TableSlot`, `EmployeeReadiness`
- Table name: `pp_<plural_snake_case>` — `pp_table_slots`, `pp_employee_readiness`
- Lookup entity: `<Name>Entity` suffix — `PreCheckStatusEntity`, `NotationTypeEntity`

## DTOs
- Request: `<Action><Entity>Request` — `CreatePreShiftCheckRequest`
- Response: `<Entity>ResponseDto` — `PreShiftCheckResponseDto`
- Use mutable classes (not records) — DTOs may be modified during algorithm-heavy processing

## Enums
- Enum class: singular noun — `PreCheckStatus`, `NotationType`
- Enum constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE` — `NOT_STARTED`, `IN_PROGRESS`

## Services & Controllers
- Service: `<Entity>Service` — `PreShiftCheckService`
- Controller: `<Entity>Controller` — `PreShiftCheckController`
- Repository: `<Entity>Repository` — `PreShiftCheckRepository`
- Mapper: `<Entity>Mapper` — `PreShiftCheckMapper`

## External Service Clients
- Client: `<ServiceName>ServiceClient` — `EmployeeServiceClient`, `RosterServiceClient`
- Name by **service**, not by entity — one client class per external service
- DTOs: group under `dtos/<service-abbreviation>/` — `dtos/eis/`, `dtos/roster/`
- Shared DTOs (e.g., `PagedResponse<T>`) live in root `dtos/` package

## Database Columns
- Primary key column: `pk_<entity>`
- Foreign key column: `fk_<referenced_entity>`
